<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 p-3 md:p-6 transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">

    <!-- Esercizio 1 IMPARARE TUTTI -->
    <div class="p-5 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl border-3 border-yellow-400 dark:border-yellow-500">
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
        <%= imparare_tutti_badge(1) %>
        Risolvi i problemi seguendo le indicazioni.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Problema a -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">a.</span>
              Lorenzo ha letto i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 4, den: 5 %> di un libro di 250 pagine. Quante pagine ha già letto?
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              Trova i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 4, den: 5 %> di 250.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-3 pl-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">250 : 5 =</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-cyan-500">→</span>
                <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 1, den: 5 %>
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">del numero totale di pagine del libro</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="50" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">× 4 =</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="200" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-cyan-500">→</span>
                <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 4, den: 5 %>
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">del numero totale di pagine del libro, cioè le pagine lette</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="200 pagine" class="flex-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p206/p206_05.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-1", alt: "Bambino che legge" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema b -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">b.</span>
              La zia ha preparato 84 bignè per il compleanno di Elisa. Quelli alla crema sono i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 5, den: 12 %> del totale.
              Calcola quanti sono i bignè alla crema.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
              Trova i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 5, den: 12 %> di
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="84" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-3 pl-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="84" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">:</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="12" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">=</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="7" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-cyan-500">→</span>
                <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 1, den: 12 %>
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">del numero totale dei bignè</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="7" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">×</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="5" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">=</span>
                <input type="text" data-correct-answer="35" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
                <span class="text-cyan-500">→</span>
                <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 5, den: 12 %>
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">del numero totale dei bignè, cioè i bignè alla crema</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 font-bold">Risposta:</span>
              <input type="text" data-correct-answer="35 bignè" class="flex-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <%= image_tag "nvi4_mat/p206/p206_05.jpg", class: "max-w-full h-auto dark:bg-white dark:rounded-lg dark:p-1", alt: "Bignè" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 2 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(2) %>
        Colora la casella con le operazioni che risolvono il problema. Poi calcola.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Problema a -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">a.</span>
            Giovanni possiede € 1 350 e decide di spendere per una vacanza a Londra i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 7, den: 15 %> di questa cifra. Quanti euro spende?
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2a" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">7 × 15 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ : 1 350 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2a" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1 350 : 7 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ × 15 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2a" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1 350 : 15 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ × 7 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2a" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1 350 : 15 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ + 7 = ........</span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Calcolo: 1 350 : 15 =</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="90" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">× 7 =</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="630" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">euro</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problema b -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">b.</span>
            Gli spettatori di un cinema occupano i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 9, den: 12 %> dei 216 posti disponibili. Quanti sono gli spettatori?
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2b" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">216 : 9 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ × 12 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2b" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">216 : 12 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ × 9 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2b" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">216 : 12 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ + 9 = ........</span>
            </label>
            <label class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-3 bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg cursor-pointer hover:bg-cyan-50 dark:hover:bg-cyan-900 has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-200 dark:has-[:checked]:bg-cyan-800">
              <input type="radio" name="es2b" class="absolute inset-0 opacity-0 cursor-pointer" data-correct-answer="false">
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">216 × 9 = ........</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">........ : 216 = ........</span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Calcolo: 216 : 12 =</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="18" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">× 9 =</span>
            <input type="text" data-correct-answer="162" class="w-16 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 text-center font-bold bg-transparent dark:text-white">
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">spettatori</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Esercizio 3 -->
    <div>
      <p class="font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mb-4">
        <%= numero_esercizio_badge(3) %>
        Risolvi i problemi sul quaderno.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">a.</span>
            Lo zio di Betty ha vinto € 1 176. Ha deciso di donarne i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 3, den: 8 %> in beneficenza. Quanti euro donerà?
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
            <span class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">b.</span>
            Il papà sistema i <%= render 'shared/frazione', num: 3, den: 5 %> dei libri che possiede nel suo studio. Se i libri sono in tutto 175, quanti ne ha sistemati?
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
